text: Muzaffargarh is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Muzaffargarh may also refer to: *Muzaffargarh District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan). *Muzaffargarh Tehsil, a tehsil of district Muzaffargarh. *Muzaffargarh railway station, a railway station in Pakistan. ==See also== * Muzaffarabad (disambiguation) * Muzaffarpur, in Bihar, India * *
